      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project car or a basic point-A-to-point-B commuter. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor dings, and fading in the clear coat, while the interior has some upholstery wear and staining from regular use. Mechanically, it starts and runs, though it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it at its best. It\u2019s a functional, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option.",
