      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting meticulous ownership and an uncompromising maintenance history. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to the highest standards of preservation, offering a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
